# Live capture reports (SCP03 live runs, eIM dumps, ...). These can
# contain derived session keys, chaining values, and IMSI/IMSI-mapped
# traces. Keep them out of git so they cannot be pushed by accident.
# `reports/.gitkeep` survives so the layout is documented.
reports/*
!reports/.gitkeep

# Packaging metadata written by `pip install -e .`
yggdrasim.egg-info/

# --- V2 universal GUI (R2-004) -------------------------------------------
# V2 work-in-progress: keep the entire GUI implementation surface off v1
# pushes so main stays exactly the v1 footprint until the GUI feature
# lands officially. Remove these rules when R2-004 graduates to `landed`
# in V2_ROADMAP.md. Design docs (V2_UNIVERSAL_GUI_PLAN.md) are not
# ignored — only the code tree.
gui_frontend/
yggdrasim_common/gui_server/
tests/test_gui_*.py